Compass | New York, NY | Full-Time | Onsite | https://www.compass.com/

We are looking for mid-level to senior-level frontend and backend candidates (tech-agnostic)!

We use a combination of:

-Angular

-React

-TypeScript

-Node

-Go

-Java

-Python

Come join a mature, mission-based startup that is aggressively growing and has secured a sizable amount of funding. We are aiming to make our mark on the real estate industry and would love your help in achieving that. Check out our careers page (https://www.compass.com/careers/) and if you're interested, feel free to send any questions to nathan.miranda@compass.com.
